 &ldquo;Have a clarity of vision but a flexibility of process&rdquo; &ndash; Jon Stewart &ldquo;Your stories matter&rdquo; &ndash; Lin-Manuel Miranda &ldquo;It&rsquo;s never too late to be the kind of person you want to be&rdquo; &ndash; Bojack Horseman &ldquo;What&rsquo;s next?&rdquo; &ndash; Jed Bartlett  I care about &hellip;
